##Workflow: Network Protocol Attacks

Setup → Recon → ARP Spoof → SMB Relay → Analysis → Report

Setup → Start VM → Configure tools → Set IP forwarding

Recon → Nmap scan → Identify targets → Find SMB services

ARP Spoof → Ettercap launch → Target selection → MITM established

SMB Relay → Responder start → LLMNR poison → Capture NTLM hashes

Analysis → Wireshark capture → Filter traffic → Extract credentials

Report → Google Docs → Log attacks → 50-word summary
